Package au.edu.anu.twcore.experiment.runtime

Interface EddWritable

All Known Subinterfaces:
IEdd
All Known Implementing Classes:
ExperimentDesignDetails
public interface EddWritable
Writable interface for ExperimentDesignDetails implementation.

Only the Experiment has access to this interface in order to construct the various collections of data.

Author:
Ian Davies - 13 Jul 2022

  • Method Details

    • factors

      Map<String,​ExpFactor> factors()
      Returns an editable map of experiment factors (ExpFactor). The map 'key' is the alias name of the factor, that is the edge Id between the Treatment node and the Field being manipulated in the configuration graph.
      Returns:
      editable map of experiment factors (ExpFactor).

    • treatments

      List<List<au.edu.anu.rscs.aot.graph.property.Property>> treatments()
      Returns an editable list of properties: one list for each simulator. Each simulation sets its property (constants) values to the properties in the list after initialization.
      Returns:
      Editable list of Properties and their values.

    • baseline

      Map<String,​Object> baseline()
      Returns an editable list of simulator constants. This list is built by the simulator when first initialized. The values may be subsequently changed by the experiment treatments following initialization.
      Returns:
      Editable list of baseline values for these simulators.
